slide5Text1: One of the tragedies of the design scene is that it always acts too late
slide5Text12: He takes snapshots, makes notes and records impressions on tablecloths or newspapers, on backs of envelopes or matchbooks. Why one thing and not another is part of the mystery, but he is omnivorous.
